result.title: [HackerRank] 101 Hack Nov'14
result.content:
Hello Coders,

The November edition of 101 Hack is here. This time we have 5 interesting challenges lined up for you. The contest commences on 29th Nov 2014 at 13:30 UTC, and will run for 2 hours. You can sign up for the contest here.

The problem statements will be available in English, Russian and Chinese.
